    "description": "我们想向您推荐一款独特的寻宝任务模拟器，拥有一个开放世界和一个基于真实事件的激动人心的故事情节。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383780/extras/469b23c64ef19cd578583c06efc37c81.poster.avif?t=1711464188\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383780/extras/469b23c64ef19cd578583c06efc37c81.webm?t=1711464188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383780/extras/469b23c64ef19cd578583c06efc37c81.mp4?t=1711464188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《Treasure Hunter》是一款金属探测模拟器，具有许多幽默的任务和一个扣人心弦的故事情节。玩家将扮演一名金属探测者，踏上一场冒险，穿越风景如画的东欧乡村，特别是古老的地区“Monastyrskaya Sloboda” - 一个充满传奇历史的地方。这片土地居住着善良的人们，他们与这片历史悠久的非凡之地分享着许多故事和秘密。您将参与各种任务，在游戏独特的开放世界中遇到许多角色。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383780/extras/d43d1929b5c563f349c2dba87efec0f1.poster.avif?t=1711464188\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383780/extras/d43d1929b5c563f349c2dba87efec0f1.webm?t=1711464188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383780/extras/d43d1929b5c563f349c2dba87efec0f1.mp4?t=1711464188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏拥有数百个埋在地下的独特发现，使玩家可以在广阔的开放世界中发现超过25万个物品。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383780/extras/fb1b5939912ed52850c8c845cf99cd70.poster.avif?t=1711464188\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383780/extras/fb1b5939912ed52850c8c845cf99cd70.webm?t=1711464188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383780/extras/fb1b5939912ed52850c8c845cf99cd70.mp4?t=1711464188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《Treasure Hunter》还设有一个装备商店，帮助提高您寻宝的效率。帮助村民解决任务，获得奖励，升级您的装备，发现有趣的地点，并挖掘稀有的发现。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383780/extras/c9d4bf68eb23601792e0a4143b6b857c.poster.avif?t=1711464188\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383780/extras/c9d4bf68eb23601792e0a4143b6b857c.webm?t=1711464188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383780/extras/c9d4bf68eb23601792e0a4143b6b857c.mp4?t=1711464188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>探索广阔的开放世界，“Monastyrskaya Sloboda”的庞大地图确保您的脚永远不会感到无聊。如果您想避免膝盖不适，建议找一辆车。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383780/extras/b110b67bf49e4079223476d7fdd4c189.poster.avif?t=1711464188\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383780/extras/b110b67bf49e4079223476d7fdd4c189.webm?t=1711464188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2383780/extras/b110b67bf49e4079223476d7fdd4c189.mp4?t=1711464188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
